### 14. Try to comment on unpublished post (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/UNPUBLISHED_POST_ID/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Trying to comment on unpublished post"
}

### 15. Try to create comment without authentication (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This should fail without auth"
}

### 16. Try to edit someone else's comment (should fail)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ANOTHER_USER_TOKEN

{
  "content": "Trying to edit someone else's comment"
}
